OL,3,CBridgend hospital has been 'left to
OL,4,Crot', staff member claims
OL,6,FThe Princess of Wales Hospital in
OL,7,FBridgend has been "left to rot" and
OL,8,Fmajor issues with the building have
OL,9,Fbeen ignored for many years, according
OL,10,Fto several hospital staff.
OL,12,FThe health board responsible for the
OL,13,Fleaking building declared a critical
OL,14,Fincident at the start of October after
OL,15,Fit said a survey discovered rot in the
OL,16,Fbeams which support the roof, with
OL,17,Falmost 200 patients initially affected.
